      <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="situation-2-synthetic-content-marking-article-50-2"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Providers of generative AI systems must ensure outputs are marked in a machine-readable format and detectable as artificially generated or manipulated. This applies to text, images, audio, and video.</p></div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="situation-3-emotion-recognition-and-biometric-cate">
