    <div class="faq-a" id="what-should-i-do-first-to-prepare"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Start with an AI tool inventory. Vision Compliance found that 83% of organizations have no formal inventory of the AI systems they use or deploy. Without an inventory, you cannot classify risk, identify gaps, or build a compliance plan. After the inventory, classify each tool by risk level, request compliance documentation from vendors, and begin implementing disclosure mechanisms for limited-risk tools.</p></div></div>
